---
title: Brown Sugar-Glazed Pork Chops with Garlic Herb Couscous and Roasted Zucchini
description: Think this is just another pork chop dinner? Think again! Here, juicy chops are coated in a sweet-and-savory glaze that’s so good...you might just lick the plate. Brown sugar provides a hint of sweetness while dijon balances it out with a tangy kick. To round it all out, we’re serving up sides of tender roasted zucchini and fluffy garlic herb couscous. Get ready for a flavor explosion.
